%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcDBD6G.jpg&h=08e0d174&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3149fe85cc59604bf7c24e3fd0c06243d5676030","tid":1303270,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T14:30:30.000Z","msg":"I highly recommend Ramen Menya in Shinjuku. They provide a range of broths to tempt demanding palates including chicken broth, pork bone broth, fish broth, miso broth and lastly spicy broth. The spicy broth is toned down to suit the palates of the tourists. Of course they too serve food adapted for their own palate. The richness of broth is perfect which will please sophisticated palates. The noodle texture is outstanding that can please the most refined palate. I highly recommend it. Another restaurant that I recommend is BBQ Fuji in Shinjuku. They serve the best quality of meat 🥩 in Japan 🇯🇵 You can choose any cuts of beef you like for barbecue such as t-bone, sirloin, ribeye, tenderloin, rump, flank, round steak and so forth as I&rsquo;m sure you all have a discriminating palate. The meat texture is of top quality which will please demanding palates. Their barbecue equipment is of high quality because the food doesn&rsquo;t stick to the grill. It&rsquo;s not like ordinary grills on which you try to flip food and it will not come loose. It sticks and tears, makes a mess and results in dry charred meat. It&rsquo;s a good bet that the yen 💴 will continue falling over the next five and a half weeks so you might as well go on holiday in Japan this year. I like Japanese culture and food. I even took the JLPT at N two level in which I got a merit. My speaking and writing far outshine my reading 📖 so the marks I lost in reading was offset by the marks I gained in writing and speaking. My friend too took the test at N three level. His listening is a little weaker while his reading is strong. Therefore the marks he gained in reading offset the marks he lost in listening. I remember I spent money on clothes and shoes like it was going out of fashion. I entered a casino 🎰 and gambled like it was going out of fashion🤣If you enjoy being in Japan you might spend money on food and cosmetic products like it&rsquo;s going out of fashion. If you enter a casino 🎰 you might gamble like it&rsquo;s going out of fashion like I did😆Going to Japan on vacation this summer is your best bet since the yen has dropped significantly. If you traveling there feel free to share your photos."},{"pid":"d9d4252643abb80622e47af5816df0cd414df951","tid":1303270,"uid":271766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:46:14.000Z","msg":"本來想講鰹之一滴<br />\n日本人打骰<br />\n但原來執咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知係搬咗定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df94dc74bbef99e0422d1a5e48ad32eca0d4c84b","tid":1303270,"uid":125477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:23:46.000Z","msg":"邊度有得買辣煌尚"},{"pid":"a00b9ac3cd2f752398beb4f42c87351cdcbce4d3","tid":1303270,"uid":281138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:16:46.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣ramen jo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}